6:30pm - Tech News with Adam and Eve Cogan (live from SSW Sydney).
Then "Agentic RAG retrieval with Microsoft FoundaryIQ: More speed & accuracy for your RAG searches" with Priyanka Shah live from SSW Brisbane!

About Priyanka!

I'm an accomplished AI expert with over 10 years of experience, currently leading AI Practice at Avanade across Southeast Asia. Honored with the CHANNEL ASIA WOMEN IN TECHNOLOGY 2023 award and a three-time Microsoft AI MVP, my expertise spans generative AI, large language models, vector databases, deep learning, neural networks and AI/ML. I've led the first enterprise integration of Generative AI in SEA, working with Azure Open AI and other open-source tools. 

Passionate about applying AI to solve intricate business issues like knowledge mining, sustainability, and ethical AI, my work crosses sectors like government, retail, and energy. In addition to my hands-on work, I actively share my insights as a public speaker and blogger, focusing on AI/ML topics. I mentor and train teams for AI hackathons and am deeply involved in AI R&D. My mission is to optimize business processes through AI and IoT and empower others to seize the limitless possibilities these technologies offer.
